snippet.title: Speedrun The Game Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Speedrun The Game... the game that you speedrun. It's kinda self explanatory. I'm so excited to release this and can't wait to see other peoples' speedrun times :).

GAME LINK: https://proliffy.itch.io/stg

CHARACTERS-
The Player (You)
Princess GG (The Princess)
The Bad Guy (The Bad Guy)
Widget and Bridget (The Bad Guy's Henchmen)

MUSIC-
"Overcast" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
